ancy and ensure database maintainability.   5️⃣ Peek Behind the Curtain: The EXPLAIN command is your oracle for query execution analysis. Use it to uncover bottlenecks and inefficiencies.   6️⃣ Batch It Up: When dealing with large datasets, batch processing shines, so you don\'t get bogged down with row-by-row operations.   7️⃣ Constant Vigilance: Monitoring and profiling are your allies. Keep a watchful eye on database performance and profile your queries to catch and fix inefficiencies.   Remember, the art of SQL optimization is all about finding the balance between query speed and resource utilization. It\'s a journey, not a destination. Let\'s ignite the discussion and share your SQL optimization stories! ?','2023-11-06 23:33:38'),('07e04b93-bd2c-4edd-a82c-34e662c62429','YouTube Data Analysis (End-To-End Data Engineering Project) ',NULL,'What will you learn? ✅ Python and PySpark ✅ SQL ✅ How to understand the business problem ✅ AWS Services - Athena, Glue, Redshift, S3, IAM ✅ Building Data Pipeline and Scheduling it','2023-11-06 22:56:24'),('0f5524c6-6ed8-44db-8f56-fc4e4afc0655','Ready to dive into the world of coding? ?',NULL,'Entering this path might seem challenging, but we\'ve compiled our top tips and tricks to guide you forward. ??  Dedication and persistence are essential when transitioning to a developer role. With a thirst for knowledge, you can reach your coding goals.  Anyone has the potential to become a coder, so the key is to remain persistent and continue sharpening your skills. ⚡️  Good luck on your journey!  How did you get your first developer job? Tell us about it in the comment section. ??','2023-11-06 23:44:23'),('1301f3eb-e34a-4295-8370-e5c1c5d8c4af','Bố của ngôn tình 9',NULL,'Anh muốn giúp có gì đâu mà dỗi Chỉ tiện đường nên han hỏi vậy thôi Hạt mưa đâu sa ướt mắt em rồi Nắng lạc đường tô hồng đôi má nhỏ  Rồi bóng dáng khuất giữa lòng phố xá Bỏ lại anh xao xuyến biết bao nhiêu Tia nắng nhỏ sao rực trời mùa hạ Một thoáng nhìn mà cũng hóa tìn